    {
      "id": "PopularPost218082",
      "post_content": "I'm all for seeing someone die from their own [Blightsteel Colossus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blightsteel Colossus) thanks to this card. I would like to point out, though, that while [Boros Fury-Shield](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boros Fury-Shield) is similar, Mirror Strike has the *creature* deal damage to its controller, whereas the Fury-Shield deals the damage, so Mirror Strike will poison out the controller of Blightsteel Colossus, whereas Fury-Shield just deals 11 damage.",
      "posted_by": "sarroth",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost218082\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">I'm all for seeing someone die from their own <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Blightsteel Colossus\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blightsteel Colossus\">Blightsteel Colossus</a> thanks to this card. I would like to point out, though, that while <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Boros Fury-Shield\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boros Fury-Shield\">Boros Fury-Shield</a> is similar, Mirror Strike has the <i>creature</i> deal damage to its controller, whereas the Fury-Shield deals the damage, so Mirror Strike will poison out the controller of Blightsteel Colossus, whereas Fury-Shield just deals 11 damage.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '218082'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy20957\">sarroth</span>\r\n                                (12/29/2011 10:55:06 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05